    "rationale": "All three primary QoIs satisfy pre-established acceptance bounds (percent difference <10%, E/uval < 1.96). Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2 vs required 3) is accepted given the regulatory standard mandates the single ASTM F1717 configuration and no additional loading scenarios are within scope of the current submission. Overall credibility is sufficient to support the Medium assurance level required for this Class II device submission.",
